@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gpiaot(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(0.77)
    v0 = wp.abs((v0 * wp.cos(v2 + 0.34)))
    tmp = (0.33 - (0.24 - 0.68))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.43) + (v1 + 0.33 / v0 + 0.99)) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.89) + (tmp + 0.02 + v1 + 0.17)))
    data[tid] = v0
